1. Install Terraform in Windows [https://www.terraform.io/downloads]
    Create Binary folder in C drive -> Paste Terraform binary file here .exe
    Advanced System Settings -> Environment variables -> Path -> edit -> browse -> select binary folder
    Relaunch command prompt
    $ terraform

2. Install on Linux {Direct commands are available}

3. Install Vs code
   Install Extension  - Terraform

4. Create New User in AWS  - permission -Administration Access

   click on User - Security credential - Generate access key - CLI - Next -Create

5. Install AWS CLI in Machine

6. aws configure

7. Plugin will store inside .terraform folder - providers folder - registry.terraform.io folder - hashicorp folder -aws folder - 4.0.0 folde - 


